, 05 Jun 2020 09:18:00 +0000</pubDate><link>https://www.dashboard.kbritokyo.jp/laporan-bulanan-ekonomi-jepang/2020-06-05</link><guid isPermaLink="false">5f22fce7761d993010e10d65:5f422f60a4e40060b3ba754a:5f4234423a7875569009e127</guid><description><![CDATA[Pemerintah Jepang memperpanjang durasi keadaan darurat sesuai dengan Act on 
