as di pasar keuangan. Pemerintah mengharapkan Bank of Japan dapat mencapai target stabilitas harga sebesar 2%.</p><p class="">Untuk laporan selengkapnya, silakan baca <a href="https://www5.cao.go.jp/keizai3/getsurei-e/reference/reference20200605.pdf"><span>di sini</span></a>.</p>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>30 April 2020</title><dc:creator>Tim Website 2020 KBRI</dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2020 09:04:00 +0000</pubDate><link>https://www.dashboard.kbritokyo.jp/laporan-bulanan-ekonomi-jepang/2020-04-30</link><guid isPermaLink="false">5f22fce7761d993010e10d65:5f422f60a4e40060b3ba754a:5f4230970f73c2195e01b15e</guid><description><![CDATA[Pemerintah Jepang mendeklarasikan status darat yang berdasarkan atas Act on 
